# ============================================
# IMPORTANT NOTES:
# ============================================
# 1. This file MUST be in the same directory as your Dockerfile
# 2. Patterns are relative to the build context directory
# 3. Use ! to explicitly include files that match exclude patterns
# 4. Order matters - later patterns override earlier ones
# 5. Always test after changes: docker build . --no-cache